<div class="block block-about">
  <div class="container">
    <a id="about" class="anchor"></a>
    <h2 class="block-title">What is BarCamp?</h2>
      <p class="lead alert alert-warning text-center">
        <a href="" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#registration-form">Register now</a> for BarCamp Green Bay 2014 and join <strong><%= User.count %></strong> other campers!
      </p>
      <p>This free event is entirely produced by <strong>you</strong>, the participants, so chances are if you are an attendee you are also a speaker. The topics tend to be somewhat tech-focused, but anyone and everyone is welcome and encouraged to attend and present on whatever they find fascinating.</p>
      <p>Check out <a href="https://plus.google.com/photos/+ChrisJaure/albums/5947313045468361489" target="_blank">photos from BarCamp Green Bay 2013</a>! If you have any questions, feel free to <a href="mailto:info@barcampgb.org">send an email</a>.</p>
      <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span4">
          <h3>How does it work?</h3>
          <p>A typical BarCamp starts off with participant collaboration on <a href="https://plus.google.com/photos/+ChrisJaure/albums/5947313045468361489/5947314505322668098?pid=5947314505322668098&oid=106571931916635496454" target="_blank">the session grid</a>, which is broken up into 45-minute blocks. Propose a talk, discussion, demo, workshop… whatever works for you!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="span4">
          <h3>Give a talk? Really?</h3>
          <p>Hey, if presenting isn’t your thing, that's cool. We understand, but we ask that you find another way to contribute, like helping with set-up or keeping the conference area tidy.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="span4">
          <h3>What about topics?</h3>
          <p>Here are some ideas from past events: 3d printing, hacker/makerspaces, survival, Minecraft, retro gaming, AI, emotional intelligence, and web development.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span4">
          <h3>Code of Conduct</h3>
          <p>BarCamp Green Bay is dedicated to a harassment-free conference experience for everyone. Please read our <%= link_to('code of conduct', 'code-of-conduct') %>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="span4">
          <h3>KidsCamp</h3>
          <p>This year we'll be organizing a <strong>KidsCamp</strong> with fun things for children to do so bring yours along and encourage them to present too!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="span4">
          <h3>Nodeschool Wisconsin</h3>
          <p>Come for Nodeschool Wisconsin's first event and learn you some node! For more information, check out <a href="http://nodeschool.io/">nodeschool.io</a> and <a href="http://nodeschool.io/wisconsin/">Nodeschool Wisconsin</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>